WEBVTT

00:07:28.157 --> 00:07:30.115
and redistributing power

00:07:30.115 --> 00:07:32.840
can be a logistical nightmare,

00:07:32.840 --> 00:07:35.129
and there's where technology can play

00:07:35.129 --> 00:07:37.306
an incredibly helpful role,

00:07:37.306 --> 00:07:40.388
by making it easier for people to organize,

00:07:40.388 --> 00:07:42.452
communicate and make decisions

00:07:42.452 --> 00:07:44.690
without having to be in the same room

00:07:44.690 --> 00:07:46.952
at the same time.

00:07:46.952 --> 00:07:48.853
Unfortunately for us,

00:07:48.853 --> 00:07:51.879
when it comes to fostering democratic processes,

00:07:51.879 --> 00:07:54.964
our city governments have not used technology

00:07:54.964 --> 00:07:57.942
to its full potential.

00:07:57.942 --> 00:08:01.159
